en though in the environment of\nconvergence, companies also need focus on self-innovation, rather than only\nadapt to the new industry evolution trend.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 Mar 2014 23:34:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-03-19"}
